<item>
            <title>[SOLR-4695] Fix core admin SPLIT action to be useful with non-cloud setups</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-4695</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The core admin SPLIT action assumes that the core being split is zookeeper aware. It will throw a NPE if invoked against a non-cloud solr setup.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;It should be fixed to work with non-cloud setups and documents in such an index should be distributed alternately into sub-indexes instead of using hashes.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
